{"tid":1984361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"簽名師入來 - 討伐中共關鍵五日","createTime":"2020-04-22T11:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T13:10:18.000Z","uid":235257,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a94ac5b6a1fc3c611886a560e6773634855a2ee","tid":1984361,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:52:43.000Z","msg":"最後五日了，最後五日機會，證明香港不是中共。這聯署表面上是希望美國順道為香港向中共追討武漢肺炎帶來的損失，實際上是證明香港站在西方世界的一邊討伐中共。<br />\n<br />\n大家快來簽名，證明香港人反共的決心。簽完也煩請幫忙share出去，讓更多人簽名。<br />\n<br />\n#簽名師召喚<br />\n#聯署師召喚 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrcPAyM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrcPAyM.png&h=8c7cd7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/b8yzwQrwz9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fb8yzwQrwz9&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=eeed8e5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/b8yzwQrwz9</a>"},{"pid":"fdf7c9bb257f8496b3af434ad0991b1b0969b763","tid":1984361,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"最後三日至啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a71195c35af53126f1e75f6d90e2f48872365b","tid":1984361,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CikUMGe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCikUMGe.jpg&h=f8954325&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2446b6f1693117384ea84c5856a80c2618113cb","tid":1984361,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:55:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9c2a548e5fdf7ea4a2f55a4b1c1f65035afa239","tid":1984361,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RHp2Vz0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRHp2Vz0.jpg&h=7453663e&s={SIZE}\" />"},